{"ts":"2026-06-27T07:38:30.133Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Inspecting The Consistency**\n\nI've confirmed the `adminSidebarLinks` entry with `id: \"support\"` correctly maps to `/admin/support`, which aligns precisely with our target page `/admin/support/page.tsx`. Everything appears consistent.\n\n\n**Planning The Interface**\n\nI am now focusing on the user interface design for the `/admin/support/page.tsx` component. I envision an enterprise-level, premium feel for 2026. Key elements include an interactive countdown for SLAs, robust search with filtering options, and real-time admin actions updating both the ticket view and secure logs. Moreover, an interactive chat wire and a modular form for simulating new support tickets with a human-centric approach will be included!\n\n\n**Drafting The Page Code**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in drafting the complete page code, starting with all the necessary imports for the React component. I am meticulously ensuring perfect alignment with the UI Quality Constitution. The draft involves a focus on linked project and document previews within a drawer; the details will reveal technical specs. I've confirmed we're using standard Tailwind styles. I'm focusing on crafting a comprehensive React component, double-checking for any other necessary file modifications.\n\n\n**Refining The Component**\n\nI'm now diving deeper into the component's architecture and making code refinements. The `page.tsx` file purely exports `AdminSupportPage()`, which simplifies the imports. I'm focusing on ensuring clean React code with no TypeScript errors. The key feature is the \"Tabbed content system\" inside a drawer triggered by clicking a project ID. This drawer will contain a tabbed view with \"Wire Chat / Console,\" \"Linked Sovereign Assets\" (project and compliance document specs), and \"Technical Specs.\" The design perfectly integrates with required UI elements like the narrative timeline, interactive selector, and hover micro-interactions!\n\n\n**Structuring The Drawer**\n\nI've outlined the structure for the drawer tabs: \"WIRE CONSOLE\" for real-time messaging, \"LINKED SANDBOX ASSETS\" for project specs, and \"DIAGNOSTIC TELEMETRY\" for SLA logs. I am meticulously detailing the \"New Support Channel\" modal, including a high-fidelity layout, an overlay backdrop, and a glowing card wrapper with clear inputs. I'm also now planning out ticket ID copy implementation using state and a timed clipboard write.\n\n\n**Implementing Countdown And Chat**\n\nI'm now implementing the SLA countdown interval within `useEffect`, ensuring it correctly decrements ticket `slaSeconds` every second, handling resolved tickets gracefully. I'm also writing the message-sending logic for the Wire Console, including a text input and a Send button. Further, I've outlined the logic for auto-scrolling the chat history with `useRef`.\n\n\n**Finalizing The Chat Logic**\n\nI've implemented auto-scrolling for the chat, which is triggered by updates or ticket selection. My focus shifted to robust message sending; I've ensured a smooth experience with input validation and instant local state updates. The message includes sender info and timestamping. I'm aiming for clean and responsive user interaction. I have also written the re-assignment and status change functions.\n\n\n**Defining Ticket Management**\n\nI've completed the agent re-assignment function, updating the ticket's agent and adding a system message to the `wireFeed`. I've also finalized the ticket status update function, which includes resetting the SLA timer on resolution, and logging status changes in the `wireFeed`. These functions ensure seamless support ticket lifecycle management.\n\n\n**Adding System Messaging**\n\nI've successfully implemented system messaging to the Wire Feed! This includes detailed lifecycle transition logs for ticket status changes. The system automatically records admin actions, enhancing auditability and providing a premium user experience with detailed audit logs. This brings a robust, dynamic enterprise feel.\n\n\n**Calculating Dynamic Metrics**\n\nI'm now calculating dynamic metrics for the support dashboard. I've implemented `activeWiresCount`, `criticalSlaRiskCount`, and `delegatedPercentage` using `useMemo` to ensure real-time updates based on the `tickets` state. These calculations will drive key performance indicators in the UI. I am focusing on making the card's border to feel premium.\n\n\n**Designing Visual Enhancements**\n\nI'm now diving into the UI's visual design. I'm prioritizing dynamic sparkline SVGs for real telemetry visualization, integrating glowing radar indicators for active streams, and applying subtle background glow effects. I'm focusing on ensuring these elements contribute to a premium, enterprise-level aesthetic. I need to make sure the custom sparklines are responsive and visually striking. I must check for compilation or type issues by running `npm run build` once I'm done. Finally, I'm reviewing the required fields and filters, including support queue, client, priority, and assigned agent.\n\n\n**Outlining The Support Page**\n\nI'm now outlining the styling details to ensure the support page exudes a premium feel. I envision Lucide icons, monospace labels, and bold sans headlines. A custom hero visual, the `PrivatePageHeader`, will be at the top with a title, subtitle, and action buttons. I will also construct an active support wire queue, a filtering panel with custom dark selects, and an interactive modal.\n\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T07:38:30.147Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"qb6wine5","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/support/page.tsx","old_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React from \"react\";\nimport { SlaTicketsTab } from \"../admin-tabs-part2\";\n\nexport default function AdminSupportPage() {\n  return <SlaTicketsTab />;\n}","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useMemo, useEffect, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { \n  Search, Plus, X, Check, Clock, Radio, Shield, \n  MessageSquare, Send, User, Folder, FileText, \n  ChevronRight, AlertCircle, CheckCircle2, RotateCcw, \n  UserCheck, AlertTriangle, Terminal, Info, Copy, CheckCircle\n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport { PrivatePageHeader } from \"@/components/private-app\";\n\n// ==========================================\n// 1. DATA MODELS & TYPES\n// ==========================================\ninterface Ticket {\n  id: string;\n  subject: string;\n  client: string;\n  priority: \"P1\" | \"P2\" | \"P3\";\n  category: \"Infrastructure\" | \"Enclave Security\" | \"Model Drift\" | \"API Gateway\" | \"Compliance Audit\";\n  status: \"OPEN\" | \"INVESTIGATING\" | \"RESOLVED\" | \"HOLD\";\n  assignedAgent: string;\n  linkedProjectId: string; // matches MOCK_PROJECTS\n  linkedDocId: string; // matches MOCK_DOCUMENTS\n  slaSeconds: number; // seconds remaining\n  description: string;\n  createdDate: string;\n  wireFeed: {\n    id: string;\n    sender: \"client\" | \"agent\" | \"system\";\n    senderName: string;\n    text: string;\n    timestamp: string;\n  }[];\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 2. COHERENT STATIC MOCK CONFIGURATION\n// ==========================================\nconst AVAILABLE_CLIENTS = [\n  \"Apex Sovereign Group [Preview Client]\",\n  \"Global Retail Enclave [Preview Client]\",\n  \"Sovereign Logistics Unit [Preview Client]\",\n  \"Federal Treasury Division [Preview Client]\",\n  \"National Health Enclave [Preview Client]\"\n];\n\nconst AVAILABLE_CATEGORIES = [\n  \"Infrastructure\",\n  \"Enclave Security\",\n  \"Model Drift\",\n  \"API Gateway\",\n  \"Compliance Audit\"\n];\n\nconst AVAILABLE_AGENTS = [\n  \"Dr. Sarah Vance\",\n  \"Alexander Mercer\",\n  \"Marcus Vance\",\n  \"Evelyn Carter\",\n  \"Unassigned\"\n];\n\nconst MOCK_PROJECTS = [\n  { id: \"PROJ-201\", name: \"Apex Sovereign Multi-Agent Lattice\", client: \"Apex Sovereign Group [Preview Client]\", enclaveType: \"Intel SGX\", phase: \"Phase V: Production-Live\", status: \"On Track\" },\n  { id: \"PROJ-202\", name: \"Global Retail Real-Time Audit Ring\", client: \"Global Retail Enclave [Preview Client]\", enclaveType: \"AMD SEV-SNP\", phase: \"Phase IV: User Acceptance Testing\", status: \"At Risk\" },\n  { id: \"PROJ-203\", name: \"Sovereign Logistics AI Route Optimizer\", client: \"Sovereign Logistics Unit [Preview Client]\", enclaveType: \"AWS Nitro Enclave\", phase: \"Phase III: Agent Alignment\", status: \"Paused\" },\n  { id: \"PROJ-204\", name: \"Federal Treasury Multi-Enclave Ledger\", client: \"Federal Treasury Division [Preview Client]\", enclaveType: \"Intel SGX\", phase: \"Phase II: Sandbox Provisioning\", status: \"Delayed\" },\n  { id: \"PROJ-205\", name: \"National Health Secure Diagnostics Loop\", client: \"National Health Enclave [Preview Client]\", enclaveType: \"AMD SEV-SNP\", phase: \"Phase I: Planning\", status: \"On Track\" }\n];\n\nconst MOCK_DOCUMENTS = [\n  { id: \"DOC-801\", title: \"Sovereign Core Architectural Blueprint\", fileSize: \"12.4 MB\", type: \"PDF\", sha256: \"0xAB9811C82FFD201A99E8F3C721A0C5E89812A\" },\n  { id: \"DOC-802\", title: \"ISO-27001 Compliance Statement\", fileSize: \"1.8 MB\", type: \"JSON\", sha256: \"0xDF1183C902ADFE33100BCCF29A8871\" },\n  { id: \"DOC-803\", title: \"eBPF Telemetry Ruleset Definition\", fileSize: \"420 KB\", type: \"YAML\", sha256: \"0xEF0128C3982DAEFC9EAA11A29038\" }\n];\n\nconst INITIAL_TICKETS: Ticket[] = [\n  {\n    id: \"T-882\",\n    subject: \"London core node replication delay above SLA threshold\",\n    client: \"Apex Sovereign Group [Preview Client]\",\n    priority: \"P1\",\n    category: \"Infrastructure\",\n    status: \"INVESTIGATING\",\n    assignedAgent: \"Dr. Sarah Vance\",\n    linkedProjectId: \"PROJ-201\",\n    linkedDocId: \"DOC-801\",\n    slaSeconds: 862, // 14m 22s\n    description: \"High-throughput isolated core loop with secure localized kernel telemetry in the London node cluster is showing a replication latency of 145ms, which exceeds the 50ms SLA maximum limit.\",\n    createdDate: \"2026-06-27T14:30:00Z\",\n    wireFeed: [\n      { id: \"w1\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Apex Sovereign Core Dev\", text: \"We are seeing alerts on our London nodes. Replication delay spiked to 145ms.\", timestamp: \"14:30\" },\n      { id: \"w2\", sender: \"system\", senderName: \"SLA MONITOR\", text: \"Warning: SLA response threshold exceeded 50ms on Node LON-01.\", timestamp: \"14:31\" },\n      { id: \"w3\", sender: \"agent\", senderName: \"Dr. Sarah Vance\", text: \"I have established a secure dual-layer TLS handshake with the London hardware enclave. Analyzing eBPF events stream now.\", timestamp: \"14:35\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"T-881\",\n    subject: \"Request for specialized auto-scaling GPU limits\",\n    client: \"Global Retail Enclave [Preview Client]\",\n    priority: \"P2\",\n    category: \"Enclave Security\",\n    status: \"OPEN\",\n    assignedAgent: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n    linkedProjectId: \"PROJ-202\",\n    linkedDocId: \"None\",\n    slaSeconds: 11460, // 3h 11m\n    description: \"Client requests temporary override of AWS Nitro Enclave thermal boundary and memory bounds to allocate additional sparse GPU clusters during end-of-quarter auditing.\",\n    createdDate: \"2026-06-27T11:00:00Z\",\n    wireFeed: [\n      { id: \"w1\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Global Retail SecOps\", text: \"We are running a massive continuous model alignment sandbox simulation and need to bypass default GPU scaling constraints temporarily.\", timestamp: \"11:00\" },\n      { id: \"w2\", sender: \"system\", senderName: \"GATEWAY\", text: \"Request logged under secure sandbox override protocols.\", timestamp: \"11:02\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"T-880\",\n    subject: \"Cryptographic verification failure on Ledger Node 4\",\n    client: \"Federal Treasury Division [Preview Client]\",\n    priority: \"P1\",\n    category: \"Compliance Audit\",\n    status: \"OPEN\",\n    assignedAgent: \"Unassigned\",\n    linkedProjectId: \"PROJ-204\",\n    linkedDocId: \"DOC-803\",\n    slaSeconds: 345, // 5m 45s\n    description: \"Enclave telemetry reported a dual-layer TLS 1.3 socket handshake failure on node GOV-SYSTEM-G2. Continuous compliance auto-scan is currently blocking active consensus blocks.\",\n    createdDate: \"2026-06-27T15:22:00Z\",\n    wireFeed: [\n      { id: \"w1\", sender: \"system\", senderName: \"SECURE KERNEL\", text: \"CRITICAL: SHA-256 verification failed on node GOV-SYSTEM-G2. Isolation triggered.\", timestamp: \"15:22\" },\n      { id: \"w2\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Treasury Auditor Jenkins\", text: \"Node 4 has been isolated from the rest of the multi-enclave ledger. We need immediate engineering review to verify security integrity.\", timestamp: \"15:23\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"T-879\",\n    subject: \"eBPF kernel event stream audit log request\",\n    client: \"National Health Enclave [Preview Client]\",\n    priority: \"P3\",\n    category: \"Compliance Audit\",\n    status: \"RESOLVED\",\n    assignedAgent: \"Evelyn Carter\",\n    linkedProjectId: \"PROJ-205\",\n    linkedDocId: \"None\",\n    slaSeconds: 0, // Resolved\n    description: \"A request for a clean, authenticated export of all kernel-level telemetry events mapped during the last medical imaging diagnostic model validation run.\",\n    createdDate: \"2026-06-26T09:00:00Z\",\n    wireFeed: [\n      { id: \"w1\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Dr. Evelyn Ross\", text: \"Please provide the complete eBPF telemetry output for our compliance files.\", timestamp: \"09:00\" },\n      { id: \"w2\", sender: \"agent\", senderName: \"Evelyn Carter\", text: \"I have exported the securely sealed audit stream (SHA_0xDE89). Sending download link now.\", timestamp: \"10:15\" },\n      { id: \"w3\", sender: \"system\", senderName: \"AUDIT SYSTEM\", text: \"Audit log package verified, signed, and closed.\", timestamp: \"10:16\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"T-878\",\n    subject: \"Route optimizer timeout during high-dimensional run\",\n    client: \"Sovereign Logistics Unit [Preview Client]\",\n    priority: \"P2\",\n    category: \"Model Drift\",\n    status: \"HOLD\",\n    assignedAgent: \"Marcus Vance\",\n    linkedProjectId: \"PROJ-203\",\n    linkedDocId: \"None\",\n    slaSeconds: 19331, // 5h 22m 11s\n    description: \"Sovereign Logistics AI Route Optimizer reported a timeout exception inside ephemeral containerized enclaves when the parameter set exceeded 15,000 continuous target nodes.\",\n    createdDate: \"2026-06-27T08:15:00Z\",\n    wireFeed: [\n      { id: \"w1\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Sovereign Logistics Ops\", text: \"Route optimizer threw timeout during geological route scaling simulation.\", timestamp: \"08:15\" },\n      { id: \"w2\", sender: \"agent\", senderName: \"Marcus Vance\", text: \"Looking into memory allocation bounds. Suspect airgapped containerized enclaves ran out of temporary heap space.\", timestamp: \"08:30\" },\n      { id: \"w3\", sender: \"client\", senderName: \"Sovereign Logistics Ops\", text: \"Understood. Placing run on HOLD until we can adjust the heap parameters.\", timestamp: \"09:12\" }\n    ]\n  }\n];\n\n// ==========================================\n// 3. MAIN COMPONENT\n// ==========================================\nexport default function AdminSupportPage() {\n  const [tickets, setTickets] = useState<Ticket[]>(INITIAL_TICKETS);\n  const [selectedTicketId, setSelectedTicketId] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  const [copiedTicketId, setCopiedTicketId] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  const [drawerTab, setDrawerTab] = useState<\"wire\" | \"assets\" | \"diagnostic\">(\"wire\");\n  const [chatInput, setChatInput] = useState(\"\");\n  const chatEndRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\n\n  // New Support Channel Form state\n  const [isNewModalOpen, setIsNewModalOpen] = useState(false);\n  const [newSubject, setNewSubject] = useState(\"\");\n  const [newClient, setNewClient] = useState(AVAILABLE_CLIENTS[0]);\n  const [newPriority, setNewPriority] = useState<\"P1\" | \"P2\" | \"P3\">(\"P2\");\n  const [newCategory, setNewCategory] = useState<Ticket[\"category\"]>(\"Infrastructure\");\n  const [newAgent, setNewAgent] = useState(\"Unassigned\");\n  const [newProject, setNewProject] = useState(\"None\");\n  const [newDoc, setNewDoc] = useState(\"None\");\n  const [newSlaHours, setNewSlaHours] = useState(\"4\");\n  const [newDescription, setNewDescription] = useState(\"\");\n\n  // Filters state\n  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(\"\");\n  const [filterClient, setFilterClient] = useState(\"\");\n  const [filterPriority, setFilterPriority] = useState(\"\");\n  const [filterCategory, setFilterCategory] = useState(\"\");\n  const [filterStatus, setFilterStatus] = useState(\"\");\n\n  // Simulated green success banner\n  const [bannerMessage, setBannerMessage] = useState<string | null>(null);\n\n  // SLA Live Countdown logic\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const timer = setInterval(() => {\n      setTickets((prevTickets) => \n        prevTickets.map((ticket) => {\n          if (ticket.status === \"RESOLVED\" || ticket.slaSeconds <= 0) {\n            return ticket;\n          }\n          return {\n            ...ticket,\n            slaSeconds: Math.max(0, ticket.slaSeconds - 1)\n          };\n        })\n      );\n    }, 1000);\n\n    return () => clearInterval(timer);\n  }, []);\n\n  // Keyboard accessibility for Esc key closing drawer and modal\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if (e.key === \"Escape\") {\n        setSelectedTicketId(null);\n        setIsNewModalOpen(false);\n      }\n    };\n    window.addEventListener(\"keydown\", handleKeyDown);\n    return () => window.removeEventListener(\"keydown\", handleKeyDown);\n  }, []);\n\n  // Scroll chat window to bottom\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (chatEndRef.current) {\n      chatEndRef.current.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n    }\n  }, [selectedTicketId, tickets, drawerTab]);\n\n  // Selected Ticket details\n  const selectedTicket = useMemo(() => {\n    return tickets.find((t) => t.id === selectedTicketId) || null;\n  }, [tickets, selectedTicketId]);\n\n  // SLA timer display text formatter\n  const formatSla = (seconds: number, status: string) => {\n    if (status === \"RESOLVED\") return \"RESOLVED\";\n    if (seconds <= 0) return \"SLA VIOLATED\";\n    const h = Math.floor(seconds / 3600);\n    const m = Math.floor((seconds % 3600) / 60);\n    const s = seconds % 60;\n    return `${h.toString().padStart(2, \"0\")}h:${m.toString().padStart(2, \"0\")}m:${s.toString().padStart(2, \"0\")}s`;\n  };\n\n  // Dynamic statistics calculations\n  const activeWiresCount = useMemo(() => {\n    return tickets.filter((t) => t.status !== \"RESOLVED\").length;\n  }, [tickets]);\n\n  const criticalSlaRiskCount = useMemo(() => {\n    return tickets.filter((t) => t.priority === \"P1\" && t.status !== \"RESOLVED\" && t.slaSeconds < 3600).length;\n  }, [tickets]);\n\n  const delegatedPercentage = useMemo(() => {\n    const assigned = tickets.filter((t) => t.assignedAgent !== \"Unassigned\").length;\n    return tickets.length ? Math.round((assigned / tickets.length) * 100) : 0;\n  }, [tickets]);\n\n  // Filter logic\n  const filteredTickets = useMemo(() => {\n    return tickets.filter((ticket) => {\n      if (searchQuery.trim() !== \"\") {\n        const query = searchQuery.toLowerCase();\n        const matchesQuery = \n          ticket.id.toLowerCase().includes(query) ||\n          ticket.subject.toLowerCase().includes(query) ||\n          ticket.client.toLowerCase().includes(query) ||\n          ticket.description.toLowerCase().includes(query);\n        if (!matchesQuery) return false;\n      }\n      if (filterClient && ticket.client !== filterClient) return false;\n      if (filterPriority && ticket.priority !== filterPriority) return false;\n      if (filterCategory && ticket.category !== filterCategory) return false;\n      if (filterStatus && ticket.status !== filterStatus) return false;\n      return true;\n    });\n  }, [tickets, searchQuery, filterClient, filterPriority, filterCategory, filterStatus]);\n\n  // Copy support ticket identifier to clipboard\n  const handleCopyId = (e: React.MouseEvent, id: string) => {\n    e.stopPropagation();\n    navigator.clipboard.writeText(id);\n    setCopiedTicketId(id);\n    setTimeout(() => setCopiedTicketId(null), 1500);\n  };\n\n  // Admin action: Change status of a support ticket\n  const handleUpdateStatus = (ticketId: string, status: Ticket[\"status\"]) => {\n    setTickets((prevTickets) =>\n      prevTickets.map((t) => {\n        if (t.id === ticketId) {\n          const systemMsg = {\n            id: `w-sys-${Date.now()}`,\n            sender: \"system\" as const,\n            senderName: \"SECURE KERNEL\",\n            text: `Lifecycle Transition: Channel status set to ${status}.`,\n            timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: \"2-digit\", minute: \"2-digit\" })\n          };\n          return {\n            ...t,\n            status,\n            wireFeed: [...t.wireFeed, systemMsg]\n          };\n        }\n        return t;\n      })\n    );\n    showBanner(`Ticket ${ticketId} status updated to ${status}.`);\n  };\n\n  // Admin action: Re-assign ticket agent\n  const handleAssignAgent = (ticketId: string, agent: string) => {\n    setTickets((prevTickets) =>\n      prevTickets.map((t) => {\n        if (t.id === ticketId) {\n          const systemMsg = {\n            id: `w-sys-${Date.now()}`,\n            sender: \"system\" as const,\n            senderName: \"SECURE KERNEL\",\n            text: `Administrative Override: Channel engineering lead re-assigned to ${agent}.`,\n            timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: \"2-digit\", minute: \"2-digit\" })\n          };\n          return {\n            ...t,\n            assignedAgent: agent,\n            wireFeed: [...t.wireFeed, systemMsg]\n          };\n        }\n        return t;\n      })\n    );\n    showBanner(`Ticket ${ticketId} engineering lead set to ${agent}.`);\n  };\n\n  // Message sending action\n  const handleSendMessage = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!chatInput.trim() || !selectedTicketId) return;\n\n    setTickets((prev) =>\n      prev.map((t) => {\n        if (t.id === selectedTicketId) {\n          return {\n            ...t,\n            wireFeed: [\n              ...t.wireFeed,\n              {\n                id: `w-msg-${Date.now()}`,\n                sender: \"agent\",\n                senderName: \"Dr. Sarah Vance (Lead Admin)\",\n                text: chatInput.trim(),\n                timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: \"2-digit\", minute: \"2-digit\" })\n              }\n            ]\n          };\n        }\n        return t;\n      })\n    );\n    setChatInput(\"\");\n  };\n\n  // Show a momentary green feedback banner at the top\n  const showBanner = (msg: string) => {\n    setBannerMessage(msg);\n    setTimeout(() => setBannerMessage(null), 4000);\n  };\n\n  // Reset all advanced filtering parameters\n  const handleResetFilters = () => {\n    setSearchQuery(\"\");\n    setFilterClient(\"\");\n    setFilterPriority(\"\");\n    setFilterCategory(\"\");\n    setFilterStatus(\"\");\n  };\n\n  // Register / Provision a new support wire\n  const handleCreateTicket = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!newSubject.trim() || !newDescription.trim()) return;\n\n    // Determine highest ticket ID number\n    const maxNum = tickets.reduce((max, t) => {\n      const num = parseInt(t.id.split(\"-\")[1]) || 800;\n      return num > max ? num : max;\n    }, 800);\n    const newId = `T-${maxNum + 1}`;\n\n    const parsedHours = parseInt(newSlaHours) || 4;\n    const initialSeconds = parsedHours * 3600;\n\n    const newTicketObj: Ticket = {\n      id: newId,\n      subject: newSubject.trim(),\n      client: newClient,\n      priority: newPriority,\n      category: newCategory,\n      status: \"OPEN\",\n      assignedAgent: newAgent,\n      linkedProjectId: newProject,\n      linkedDocId: newDoc,\n      slaSeconds: initialSeconds,\n      description: newDescription.trim(),\n      createdDate: new Date().toISOString(),\n      wireFeed: [\n        {\n          id: \"w-sys-1\",\n          sender: \"system\",\n          senderName: \"INTEGRITY PROTOCOL\",\n          text: `Support communication line initialized under Dual-Layer TLS 1.3 socket. Unique identifier: ${newId}.`,\n          timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: \"2-digit\", minute: \"2-digit\" })\n        }\n      ]\n    };\n\n    setTickets([newTicketObj, ...tickets]);\n    setIsNewModalOpen(false);\n    showBanner(`Sovereign support wire ${newId} securely provisioned.`);\n    \n    // Reset form fields\n    setNewSubject(\"\");\n    setNewClient(AVAILABLE_CLIENTS[0]);\n    setNewPriority(\"P2\");\n    setNewCategory(\"Infrastructure\");\n    setNewAgent(\"Unassigned\");\n    setNewProject(\"None\");\n    setNewDoc(\"None\");\n    setNewSlaHours(\"4\");\n    setNewDescription(\"\");\n  };\n\n  // Connected assets details resolution\n  const connectedProject = useMemo(() => {\n    if (!selectedTicket || selectedTicket.linkedProjectId === \"None\") return null;\n    return MOCK_PROJECTS.find((p) => p.id === selectedTicket.linkedProjectId) || null;\n  }, [selectedTicket]);\n\n  const connectedDocument = useMemo(() => {\n    if (!selectedTicket || selectedTicket.linkedDocId === \"None\") return null;\n    return MOCK_DOCUMENTS.find((d) => d.id === selectedTicket.linkedDocId) || null;\n  }, [selectedTicket]);\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 relative min-h-screen text-white select-none\">\n      \n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* SIMULATED SYSTEM FEEDBACK BANNER */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {bannerMessage && (\n        <div className=\"fixed top-20 right-6 z-50 max-w-sm bg-black/90 border border-emerald-500/30 text-[12px] font-mono p-4 rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] flex items-start gap-2.5 transition-all animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top-4 duration-300\">\n          <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n          <div>\n            <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold block uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]\">INTEGRITY RE-VERIFIED</span>\n            <span className=\"text-white/80 mt-0.5 block\">{bannerMessage}</span>\n          </div>\n          <button onClick={() => setBannerMessage(null)} className=\"text-white/30 hover:text-white/60 ml-auto cursor-pointer\">\n            <X className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* PAGE HEADER */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      <PrivatePageHeader \n        title=\"Enterprise Priority Support Wires\" \n        desc=\"Admin Operations Hub. Monitor real-time SLA metrics, triage cryptographic enclaves, and assign dedicated GFF core engineers.\"\n        badgeLabel=\"SECURE SLA MONITOR\"\n        actions={\n          <>\n            <button \n              onClick={handleResetFilters}\n              className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-[11px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1.5\"\n            >\n              <RotateCcw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>Reset Filters</span>\n            </button>\n            <button \n              onClick={() => setIsNewModalOpen(true)}\n              className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[11px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(0,157,255,0.4)]\"\n            >\n              <Plus className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>Provision Support Wire</span>\n            </button>\n          </>\n        }\n      />\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* REAL-TIME DYNAMIC METRICS BOARD */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\">\n        \n        {/* Dynamic Card 1: Active Wires */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 flex items-center justify-between transition-all hover:border-white/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Active Secure Channels</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[24px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span>{activeWiresCount} Wires</span>\n              {activeWiresCount > 0 && (\n                <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n                  <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-cyan-400 opacity-75\"></span>\n                  <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-cyan-500\"></span>\n                </span>\n              )}\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Total: {tickets.length} Registered Streams</div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col items-end shrink-0 text-cyan-400/40 select-none\">\n            <Radio className=\"w-9 h-9 animate-pulse\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Dynamic Card 2: Critical SLA Risks */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 flex items-center justify-between transition-all hover:border-white/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Critical SLA Expiry Risks</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[24px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className={criticalSlaRiskCount > 0 ? \"text-amber-400 font-extrabold\" : \"text-white\"}>\n                {criticalSlaRiskCount} Extreme Risk\n              </span>\n              {criticalSlaRiskCount > 0 && (\n                <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n                  <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75\"></span>\n                  <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500\"></span>\n                </span>\n              )}\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Within 1 Hour Boundary</div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col items-end shrink-0 text-amber-400/40 select-none\">\n            <AlertTriangle className=\"w-9 h-9\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Dynamic Card 3: Assigned Engineering Coverage */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/60 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 flex items-center justify-between transition-all hover:border-white/10\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Engineering Allocation</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[24px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">{delegatedPercentage}% Delegated</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">\n              {tickets.filter((t) => t.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\").length} Unassigned Channels\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col items-end shrink-0 text-emerald-400/40 select-none\">\n            <UserCheck className=\"w-9 h-9\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* ADVANCED MULTI-LEVEL FILTERING SYSTEM */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050507]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-4\">\n        \n        <div className=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-3 items-stretch xl:items-center\">\n          \n          {/* Global Search Input */}\n          <div className=\"relative flex-grow\">\n            <Search className=\"absolute left-3.5 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-white/30\" />\n            <input \n              type=\"text\"\n              value={searchQuery}\n              onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}\n              placeholder=\"Search by SLA ticket identifier, subject, or description metrics...\"\n              className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 pl-10 pr-4 text-[12px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 outline-none focus:border-white/15 focus:bg-white/[0.03] transition-all\"\n            />\n            {searchQuery && (\n              <button \n                onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")}\n                className=\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 text-white/40 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                <X className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n              </button>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Filtering Dropdown Selectors */}\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:flex sm:flex-wrap gap-2.5\">\n            \n            {/* Filter Client */}\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select\n                value={filterClient}\n                onChange={(e) => setFilterClient(e.target.value)}\n                className=\"h-9 w-full sm:w-[190px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 px-3 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white/60\">CLIENTS (ALL)</option>\n                {AVAILABLE_CLIENTS.map((client) => (\n                  <option key={client} value={client} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white\">\n                    {client.split(\" [\")[0].toUpperCase()}\n                  </option>\n                ))}\n              </select>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Filter Priority */}\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select\n                value={filterPriority}\n                onChange={(e) => setFilterPriority(e.target.value)}\n                className=\"h-9 w-full sm:w-[120px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 px-3 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white/60\">PRIORITY (ALL)</option>\n                <option value=\"P1\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-red-400\">P1 SLA</option>\n                <option value=\"P2\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-amber-400\">P2 SLA</option>\n                <option value=\"P3\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-blue-400\">P3 SLA</option>\n              </select>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Filter Category */}\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select\n                value={filterCategory}\n                onChange={(e) => setFilterCategory(e.target.value)}\n                className=\"h-9 w-full sm:w-[160px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 px-3 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white/60\">CATEGORY (ALL)</option>\n                {AVAILABLE_CATEGORIES.map((cat) => (\n                  <option key={cat} value={cat} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white\">\n                    {cat.toUpperCase()}\n                  </option>\n                ))}\n              </select>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Filter Status */}\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select\n                value={filterStatus}\n                onChange={(e) => setFilterStatus(e.target.value)}\n                className=\"h-9 w-full sm:w-[150px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 px-3 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white/60\">STATUS (ALL)</option>\n                <option value=\"OPEN\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-cyan-400\">OPEN</option>\n                <option value=\"INVESTIGATING\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-amber-400\">INVESTIGATING</option>\n                <option value=\"HOLD\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-purple-400\">ON HOLD</option>\n                <option value=\"RESOLVED\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-emerald-400\">RESOLVED</option>\n              </select>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Active Filter Tags Helper */}\n        {(searchQuery || filterClient || filterPriority || filterCategory || filterStatus) && (\n          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 border-t border-white/5 pt-3 select-none\">\n            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-semibold\">Active Filter Bounds:</span>\n            \n            {searchQuery && (\n              <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-cyan-500/20 bg-cyan-500/5 text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400\">\n                <span>QUERY: &quot;{searchQuery}&quot;</span>\n                <X className=\"w-3 h-3 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")} />\n              </span>\n            )}\n            \n            {filterClient && (\n              <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">\n                <span>CLIENT: {filterClient.split(\" [\")[0].toUpperCase()}</span>\n                <X className=\"w-3 h-3 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" onClick={() => setFilterClient(\"\")} />\n              </span>\n            )}\n\n            {filterPriority && (\n              <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/5 text-[10px] font-mono text-red-400\">\n                <span>PRIORITY: {filterPriority}</span>\n                <X className=\"w-3 h-3 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" onClick={() => setFilterPriority(\"\")} />\n              </span>\n            )}\n\n            {filterCategory && (\n              <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5 text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400\">\n                <span>CATEGORY: {filterCategory.toUpperCase()}</span>\n                <X className=\"w-3 h-3 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" onClick={() => setFilterCategory(\"\")} />\n              </span>\n            )}\n\n            {filterStatus && (\n              <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/5 text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400\">\n                <span>STATUS: {filterStatus}</span>\n                <X className=\"w-3 h-3 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" onClick={() => setFilterStatus(\"\")} />\n              </span>\n            )}\n\n            <button \n              onClick={handleResetFilters}\n              className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:underline cursor-pointer ml-auto uppercase font-bold\"\n            >\n              Clear All Filtering Bounds\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        )}\n\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* SUPPORT TICKETS QUEUE: DESKTOP TABLE & MOBILE LIST */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      \n      {/* 1. Desktop Table Layout */}\n      <div className=\"hidden md:block border border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050507]/40 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden\">\n        <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse font-mono text-[11.5px] relative\">\n          <thead>\n            <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider select-none\">\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[100px]\">ID</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">Subject & Client</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[100px]\">Priority</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[150px]\">Category</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[140px]\">Status</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[160px]\">Assigned Engineer</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[120px]\">Assets</th>\n              <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold w-[140px] text-right\">SLA Timer</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody>\n            {filteredTickets.map((ticket) => {\n              const isSelected = selectedTicketId === ticket.id;\n              \n              // Define priority badge styles\n              const priorityStyles = {\n                P1: \"text-red-400 bg-red-400/10 border-red-400/20\",\n                P2: \"text-amber-400 bg-amber-400/10 border-amber-400/20\",\n                P3: \"text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-400/10 border-cyan-400/20\"\n              };\n\n              // Define status badge styles\n              const statusStyles = {\n                OPEN: \"text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-400/5 border-cyan-400/15\",\n                INVESTIGATING: \"text-amber-400 bg-amber-400/5 border-amber-400/15\",\n                HOLD: \"text-purple-400 bg-purple-400/5 border-purple-400/15\",\n                RESOLVED: \"text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/5 border-emerald-500/15\"\n              };\n\n              return (\n                <tr \n                  key={ticket.id}\n                  onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(ticket.id)}\n                  className={`border-b border-white/[0.03] last:border-0 hover:bg-white/[0.02] cursor-pointer transition-colors relative ${\n                    isSelected ? \"bg-white/[0.03] border-l-2 border-l-[#009DFF]\" : \"\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  {/* ID */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4 font-bold\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 group/id\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] hover:underline\">{ticket.id}</span>\n                      <button \n                        onClick={(e) => handleCopyId(e, ticket.id)}\n                        className=\"opacity-0 group-hover/id:opacity-100 p-0.5 hover:text-white text-white/40 cursor-pointer transition-opacity\"\n                        title=\"Copy Identifier\"\n                      >\n                        {copiedTicketId === ticket.id ? (\n                          <Check className=\"w-3 h-3 text-emerald-400\" />\n                        ) : (\n                          <Copy className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                        )}\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Subject & Client */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4 max-w-[320px] truncate\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold tracking-tight text-[12.5px] block truncate leading-tight\">\n                        {ticket.subject}\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40 text-[10px] block truncate uppercase\">\n                        {ticket.client.split(\" [\")[0]}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Priority */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4\">\n                    <span className={`inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded border text-[9.5px] font-bold ${priorityStyles[ticket.priority]}`}>\n                      {ticket.priority} SLA\n                    </span>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Category */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4 text-white/80\">\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 border border-white/5 rounded bg-white/[0.01] text-[10px]\">\n                      {ticket.category.toUpperCase()}\n                    </span>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Status */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4\">\n                    <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border text-[10px] font-bold ${statusStyles[ticket.status]}`}>\n                      <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${\n                        ticket.status === \"OPEN\" ? \"bg-cyan-400 animate-pulse\" :\n                        ticket.status === \"INVESTIGATING\" ? \"bg-amber-400 animate-pulse\" :\n                        ticket.status === \"HOLD\" ? \"bg-purple-400\" : \"bg-emerald-500\"\n                      }`} />\n                      <span>{ticket.status}</span>\n                    </span>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Assigned Agent */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-white/70\">\n                      <User className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 ${ticket.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\" ? \"text-white/20\" : \"text-[#009DFF]\"}`} />\n                      <span className={ticket.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\" ? \"text-white/30 italic\" : \"text-white\"}>\n                        {ticket.assignedAgent}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* Assets */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4 text-white/50\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      {ticket.linkedProjectId !== \"None\" && (\n                        <Folder className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#00FFC2]\" title={`Project: ${ticket.linkedProjectId}`} />\n                      )}\n                      {ticket.linkedDocId !== \"None\" && (\n                        <FileText className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-400\" title={`Document: ${ticket.linkedDocId}`} />\n                      )}\n                      {ticket.linkedProjectId === \"None\" && ticket.linkedDocId === \"None\" && (\n                        <span className=\"text-white/20\">-</span>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                  </td>\n\n                  {/* SLA Timer */}\n                  <td className=\"py-4 px-4 text-right\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-1.5\">\n                      {ticket.status !== \"RESOLVED\" && ticket.slaSeconds > 0 && (\n                        <Clock className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 ${\n                          ticket.slaSeconds < 3600 ? \"text-red-400 animate-pulse\" : \"text-amber-400\"\n                        }`} />\n                      )}\n                      <span className={`font-mono font-bold ${\n                        ticket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-emerald-400\" :\n                        ticket.slaSeconds <= 0 ? \"text-red-500 font-extrabold animate-pulse\" :\n                        ticket.slaSeconds < 3600 ? \"text-red-400\" : \"text-amber-400\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {formatSla(ticket.slaSeconds, ticket.status)}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                  </td>\n\n                </tr>\n              );\n            })}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 2. Mobile Cards Grid Layout */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:hidden\">\n        {filteredTickets.map((ticket) => {\n          const isSelected = selectedTicketId === ticket.id;\n          \n          return (\n            <div \n              key={ticket.id}\n              onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(ticket.id)}\n              className={`border rounded-2xl p-4 space-y-4 bg-[#050507]/60 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n                isSelected ? \"border-[#009DFF]/50 bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 hover:border-white/10\"\n              }`}\n            >\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-2\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-[10px]\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{ticket.id}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30\">•</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase\">{ticket.category}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-white font-bold tracking-tight text-[13.5px] leading-tight\">\n                    {ticket.subject}\n                  </h4>\n                </div>\n                \n                <span className={`inline-flex items-center px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border text-[8.5px] font-bold ${\n                  ticket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"text-red-400 border-red-400/20 bg-red-400/10\" :\n                  ticket.priority === \"P2\" ? \"text-amber-400 border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/10\" :\n                  \"text-cyan-400 border-cyan-400/20 bg-cyan-400/10\"\n                }`}>\n                  {ticket.priority}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3 space-y-2.5 font-mono text-[10.5px]\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-white/50\">\n                  <span>CLIENT:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white uppercase text-[9.5px] font-bold truncate max-w-[150px]\">\n                    {ticket.client.split(\" [\")[0]}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-white/50\">\n                  <span>LEAD ENGINEER:</span>\n                  <span className={ticket.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\" ? \"text-white/30 italic\" : \"text-white font-bold\"}>\n                    {ticket.assignedAgent}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-white/50\">\n                  <span>SLA TIMER:</span>\n                  <span className={`font-bold ${\n                    ticket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-emerald-400\" :\n                    ticket.slaSeconds <= 0 ? \"text-red-500 animate-pulse font-extrabold\" :\n                    ticket.slaSeconds < 3600 ? \"text-red-400\" : \"text-amber-400\"\n                  }`}>\n                    {formatSla(ticket.slaSeconds, ticket.status)}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between pt-3 border-t border-white/5\">\n                <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border text-[9.5px] font-bold ${\n                  ticket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-emerald-400 border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/5\" :\n                  ticket.status === \"HOLD\" ? \"text-purple-400 border-purple-400/20 bg-purple-400/5\" :\n                  ticket.status === \"INVESTIGATING\" ? \"text-amber-400 border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5\" :\n                  \"text-cyan-400 border-cyan-400/20 bg-cyan-400/5\"\n                }`}>\n                  <span>{ticket.status}</span>\n                </span>\n\n                <div className=\"flex gap-1.5 text-white/40\">\n                  {ticket.linkedProjectId !== \"None\" && <Folder className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />}\n                  {ticket.linkedDocId !== \"None\" && <FileText className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" />}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          );\n        })}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 3. Empty State Fallback */}\n      {filteredTickets.length === 0 && (\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-14 border border-dashed border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050507]/20 font-mono text-center select-none\">\n          <AlertCircle className=\"w-10 h-10 text-white/20 mb-3 animate-pulse\" />\n          <h4 className=\"text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">No Secure support wires found</h4>\n          <p className=\"text-white/40 text-[11px] max-w-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed\">\n            Your filtering bounds did not resolve to any priority channels. Reset filters to restore communications tracking.\n          </p>\n          <button\n            onClick={handleResetFilters}\n            className=\"mt-4 px-4 h-8 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-[10px] font-bold text-white transition-all cursor-pointer uppercase tracking-wider\"\n          >\n            Reset Filters\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* SIDE-OUT SUPPORT DETAIL DRAWER */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {selectedTicket && (\n        <>\n          {/* Drawer Overlay Backdrop */}\n          <div \n            onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)}\n            className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-40 transition-opacity\"\n          />\n\n          {/* Slide-out Panel */}\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-y-0 right-0 z-50 w-full sm:w-[500px] md:w-[600px] lg:w-[680px] bg-[#07070a]/98 border-l border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md shadow-2xl p-6 overflow-y-auto transform transition-transform duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            \n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              \n              {/* Drawer Header */}\n              <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\">\n                      {selectedTicket.id}\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-red-400 bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase\">\n                      {selectedTicket.priority} SLA\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h2 className=\"text-[16px] font-bold text-white leading-tight mt-1.5\">\n                    {selectedTicket.subject}\n                  </h2>\n                  <p className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest leading-none mt-1\">\n                    CLIENT: {selectedTicket.client}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)}\n                  className=\"p-1 rounded hover:bg-white/5 text-white/40 hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                >\n                  <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Advanced Multi-Tab Controller */}\n              <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 select-none font-mono text-[10px]\">\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setDrawerTab(\"wire\")}\n                  className={`px-4 py-2.5 border-b-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    drawerTab === \"wire\" \n                      ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-[#009DFF]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/40 hover:text-white/80\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  <MessageSquare className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                  <span>Secure Wire Console</span>\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setDrawerTab(\"assets\")}\n                  className={`px-4 py-2.5 border-b-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    drawerTab === \"assets\" \n                      ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-[#009DFF]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/40 hover:text-white/80\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  <Folder className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                  <span>Sovereign Assets ({selectedTicket.linkedProjectId === \"None\" && selectedTicket.linkedDocId === \"None\" ? 0 : (selectedTicket.linkedProjectId !== \"None\" && selectedTicket.linkedDocId !== \"None\" ? 2 : 1)})</span>\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setDrawerTab(\"diagnostic\")}\n                  className={`px-4 py-2.5 border-b-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                    drawerTab === \"diagnostic\" \n                      ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-[#009DFF]\" \n                      : \"border-transparent text-white/40 hover:text-white/80\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  <Terminal className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                  <span>Operational Diagnostics</span>\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* TAB 1: WIRE CONSOLE & MESSAGING */}\n              {drawerTab === \"wire\" && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  \n                  {/* Secure Handshake Notice */}\n                  <div className=\"border border-emerald-500/15 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/[0.02] p-3 text-[11px] font-mono text-emerald-400 flex items-start gap-2 select-text\">\n                    <Shield className=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[9px] block\">Cryptographic Dual-Layer Handshake verified</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/70 mt-0.5 block\">Communications secured with hardware isolation. eBPF kernel event tracking active.</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Wire Message History Stream */}\n                  <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-black/40 p-4 h-[280px] overflow-y-auto space-y-3 flex flex-col font-mono text-[11px] select-text\">\n                    {selectedTicket.wireFeed.map((feed) => {\n                      if (feed.sender === \"system\") {\n                        return (\n                          <div key={feed.id} className=\"text-white/30 border-b border-white/[0.02] pb-1.5 last:border-0 leading-relaxed text-[10px]\">\n                            <span className=\"text-cyan-500 font-bold\">&gt;&gt; SYSTEM LOG:</span> {feed.text}\n                            <span className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/20 ml-2\">({feed.timestamp})</span>\n                          </div>\n                        );\n                      }\n\n                      const isAgent = feed.sender === \"agent\";\n                      return (\n                        <div \n                          key={feed.id} \n                          className={`max-w-[85%] rounded-xl p-3 space-y-1 ${\n                            isAgent \n                              ? \"self-end bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-white\" \n                              : \"self-start bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 text-white/90\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/[0.02] pb-0.5 text-[9.5px]\">\n                            <span className={`font-bold ${isAgent ? \"text-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-amber-400\"}`}>\n                              {feed.senderName.toUpperCase()}\n                            </span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[8.5px]\">{feed.timestamp}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap mt-1 text-[11px] font-mono\">\n                            {feed.text}\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                    <div ref={chatEndRef} />\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Message Input Form */}\n                  <form onSubmit={handleSendMessage} className=\"flex gap-2 font-mono\">\n                    <input\n                      type=\"text\"\n                      value={chatInput}\n                      onChange={(e) => setChatInput(e.target.value)}\n                      placeholder=\"Type secure operational message...\"\n                      className=\"flex-grow h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-white/10 px-3.5 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 outline-none focus:border-white/20 focus:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all\"\n                    />\n                    <button\n                      type=\"submit\"\n                      disabled={!chatInput.trim()}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-10 shrink-0 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-all cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.2)]\"\n                    >\n                      <Send className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                    </button>\n                  </form>\n\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* TAB 2: LINKED SOVEREIGN ASSETS */}\n              {drawerTab === \"assets\" && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  \n                  {/* Linked Project details */}\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <Folder className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                      <span>Linked Integration Project</span>\n                    </h4>\n\n                    {connectedProject ? (\n                      <div className=\"border border-white/5 bg-[#020203]/40 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start\">\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold text-[12px] block leading-none\">\n                              {connectedProject.id}\n                            </span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-[13px] block mt-1.5 leading-snug\">\n                              {connectedProject.name}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] text-[#00FFC2] bg-[#00FFC2]/10 border border-[#00FFC2]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase\">\n                            {connectedProject.enclaveType}\n                          </span>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3.5\">\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase block font-semibold\">Project Status</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-bold mt-0.5 block\">{connectedProject.status}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase block font-semibold\">Sovereign Phase</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-bold mt-0.5 block\">{connectedProject.phase.split(\": \")[1]}</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    ) : (\n                      <div className=\"border border-dashed border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-white/30 text-[11px] font-mono\">\n                        No sovereign project linked to this support channel.\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Linked Document details */}\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <FileText className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" />\n                      <span>Linked Compliance Document</span>\n                    </h4>\n\n                    {connectedDocument ? (\n                      <div className=\"border border-white/5 bg-[#020203]/40 rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3.5 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start\">\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-amber-400 font-bold text-[12px] block leading-none\">\n                              {connectedDocument.id}\n                            </span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-[13px] block mt-1.5 leading-snug\">\n                              {connectedDocument.title}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] text-amber-400 bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase\">\n                            {connectedDocument.type}\n                          </span>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3 space-y-2 select-text\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[11px]\">\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30\">FILE SIZE:</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{connectedDocument.fileSize}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 uppercase block font-semibold\">Cryptographic SHA-256 Hash</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-semibold text-[9.5px] block truncate select-all\">\n                              {connectedDocument.sha256}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    ) : (\n                      <div className=\"border border-dashed border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-white/30 text-[11px] font-mono\">\n                        No compliance document linked to this support channel.\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* TAB 3: OPERATIONAL DIAGNOSTICS & SYSTEM META */}\n              {drawerTab === \"diagnostic\" && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[11px] select-text\">\n                  \n                  {/* Detailed Description Block */}\n                  <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-black/40 p-4 space-y-2\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold\">PROBLEM SPECIFICATION DETAILED DESCRIPTION</span>\n                    <p className=\"text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-[11.5px] whitespace-pre-line font-mono\">\n                      {selectedTicket.description}\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SLA Telemetry Log list */}\n                  <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#020203]/40 p-4 space-y-3\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold block\">CHRONOLOGICAL AUDIT TELEMETRY</span>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2.5 relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-1.5 before:top-1 before:bottom-1 before:w-[1px] before:bg-white/5\">\n                      <div className=\"relative\">\n                        <span className=\"absolute left-[-16px] top-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\" />\n                        <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] block\">CREATED ON EPOCH TIMESTAMP</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-semibold mt-0.5 block\">{selectedTicket.createdDate}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"relative\">\n                        <span className=\"absolute left-[-16px] top-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]\" />\n                        <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] block\">SECURITY ASSIGNMENT BOUND</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-semibold mt-0.5 block\">\n                          Engineer allocated: {selectedTicket.assignedAgent}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"relative\">\n                        <span className={`absolute left-[-16px] top-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"bg-emerald-500\" : \"bg-amber-400\"}`} />\n                        <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] block\">SLA PARAMETER MONITOR</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-semibold mt-0.5 block\">\n                          Current timer status: {formatSla(selectedTicket.slaSeconds, selectedTicket.status)}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Quick Copy Box */}\n                  <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-black/20 p-3 flex justify-between items-center select-none\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-white/50\">\n                      <Terminal className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                      <span>SECURE RECORD ENCRYPTED CRYPTOHASH</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <button \n                      onClick={(e) => handleCopyId(e, `0xSHA_${selectedTicket.id}_${selectedTicket.slaSeconds}`)}\n                      className=\"h-7 px-2 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-all flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer\"\n                    >\n                      <Copy className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                      <span>Copy Encrypted Hash</span>\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n            </div>\n\n            {/* ========================================================== */}\n            {/* ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS PANEL */}\n            {/* ========================================================== */}\n            <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/10 bg-black/[0.15] mt-6 space-y-4 select-none\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[10.5px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <Info className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                <span>ADMINISTRATIVE ACTION WIRE CONTROL PANEL (LOCAL STATE SETTINGS)</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                \n                {/* Agent Assignment Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase block font-semibold\">RE-ASSIGN LEAD ENGINEER</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={selectedTicket.assignedAgent}\n                      onChange={(e) => handleAssignAgent(selectedTicket.id, e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      {AVAILABLE_AGENTS.map((agent) => (\n                        <option key={agent} value={agent} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-white\">\n                          {agent.toUpperCase()}\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Status Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase block font-semibold\">CHANGE LIFE-CYCLE STATUS</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={selectedTicket.status}\n                      onChange={(e) => handleUpdateStatus(selectedTicket.id, e.target.value as Ticket[\"status\"])}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      <option value=\"OPEN\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-cyan-400\">OPEN</option>\n                      <option value=\"INVESTIGATING\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-amber-400\">INVESTIGATING</option>\n                      <option value=\"HOLD\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-purple-400\">ON HOLD</option>\n                      <option value=\"RESOLVED\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0e] text-emerald-400\">RESOLVED</option>\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"flex gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => handleUpdateStatus(selectedTicket.id, \"RESOLVED\")}\n                  disabled={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\"}\n                  className=\"flex-grow h-9 rounded bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold uppercase transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-45 disabled:cursor-not-allowed select-none shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]\"\n                >\n                  <CheckCircle className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                  <span>Resolve & Close SLA</span>\n                </button>\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)}\n                  className=\"px-4 h-9 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white transition-all cursor-pointer font-bold uppercase\"\n                >\n                  Close Drawer\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {/* PROVISION NEW SUPPORT WIRE MODAL */}\n      {/* ============================================================================ */}\n      {isNewModalOpen && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 select-none\">\n          \n          <div className=\"relative max-w-xl w-full bg-[#07070a] border border-white/15 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden animate-in fade-in zoom-in-95 duration-250\">\n            \n            {/* Close Button */}\n            <button \n              onClick={() => setIsNewModalOpen(false)}\n              className=\"absolute right-4 top-4 text-white/40 hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n            >\n              <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n            </button>\n\n            {/* Modal Title */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <Terminal className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-[16px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                Provision New SLA Support Wire\n              </h3>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Modal Form */}\n            <form onSubmit={handleCreateTicket} className=\"space-y-4 mt-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n              \n              {/* Ticket Subject */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">SUPPORT WIRE SUBJECT / HEADLINE</label>\n                <input \n                  type=\"text\"\n                  required\n                  placeholder=\"e.g. Memory leak warning detected in continuous model alignment\"\n                  value={newSubject}\n                  onChange={(e) => setNewSubject(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-white/10 px-3.5 text-[11.5px] text-white placeholder-white/35 outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/40 focus:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                \n                {/* Target Client Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">SOVEREIGN CLIENT</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newClient}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewClient(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      {AVAILABLE_CLIENTS.map((client) => (\n                        <option key={client} value={client} className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white\">\n                          {client.split(\" [\")[0].toUpperCase()}\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Priority Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">SLA PRIORITY LEVEL</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newPriority}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewPriority(e.target.value as \"P1\" | \"P2\" | \"P3\")}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      <option value=\"P1\" className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-red-400\">P1 SLA CRITICAL (1H)</option>\n                      <option value=\"P2\" className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-amber-400\">P2 SLA HIGH (4H)</option>\n                      <option value=\"P3\" className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-cyan-400\">P3 SLA STANDARD (12H)</option>\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                \n                {/* Category Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">CATEGORY</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newCategory}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewCategory(e.target.value as Ticket[\"category\"])}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      {AVAILABLE_CATEGORIES.map((cat) => (\n                        <option key={cat} value={cat} className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white\">\n                          {cat.toUpperCase()}\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Lead Engineer Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">LEAD ASSIGNED ENGINEER</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newAgent}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewAgent(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      {AVAILABLE_AGENTS.map((agent) => (\n                        <option key={agent} value={agent} className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white\">\n                          {agent.toUpperCase()}\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                \n                {/* SLA Hour Timer */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">SLA LIMIT (HOURS)</label>\n                  <input \n                    type=\"number\"\n                    min=\"1\"\n                    max=\"168\"\n                    value={newSlaHours}\n                    onChange={(e) => setNewSlaHours(e.target.value)}\n                    className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-3.5 text-[11.5px] text-white outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/40 transition-all\"\n                  />\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Linked Project Selection */}\n                <div className=\"col-span-2 space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">LINK SOVEREIGN ASSEMBLY PROJECT</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newProject}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewProject(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      <option value=\"None\" className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white/50\">NONE / UNASSIGNED</option>\n                      {MOCK_PROJECTS.map((proj) => (\n                        <option key={proj.id} value={proj.id} className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white\">\n                          {proj.id} - {proj.name.substring(0, 30)}...\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-3\">\n                \n                {/* Linked Compliance Document Selection */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">LINK COMPLIANCE REFERENCE DOCUMENT</label>\n                  <div className=\"relative\">\n                    <select\n                      value={newDoc}\n                      onChange={(e) => setNewDoc(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3.5 pr-8 text-[11px] text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      <option value=\"None\" className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white/50\">NONE / UNASSIGNED</option>\n                      {MOCK_DOCUMENTS.map((doc) => (\n                        <option key={doc.id} value={doc.id} className=\"bg-[#07070a] text-white\">\n                          {doc.id} - {doc.title.substring(0, 45)}...\n                        </option>\n                      ))}\n                    </select>\n                    <div className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-1.5 h-1.5 border-r border-b border-white/40 transform rotate-45 pointer-events-none\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Description Details */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase font-semibold block\">DETAILED TECHNICAL PROBLEM DESCRIPTION</label>\n                <textarea \n                  required\n                  rows={3}\n                  placeholder=\"Provide precise hardware enclave logs, API paths, and eBPF kernel exception codes...\"\n                  value={newDescription}\n                  onChange={(e) => setNewDescription(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-white/10 p-3 text-[11.5px] text-white placeholder-white/35 outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/40 focus:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all resize-none\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Action Buttons */}\n              <div className=\"flex gap-2.5 pt-2 select-none\">\n                <button\n                  type=\"submit\"\n                  className=\"flex-grow h-9 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-white font-bold uppercase transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.2)]\"\n                >\n                  <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                  <span>Provision Wire Channel</span>\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => setIsNewModalOpen(false)}\n                  className=\"px-4 h-9 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white font-bold uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  Cancel\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n            </form>\n\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
